{"type":null,"faqId":26495,"title":"荣耀畅玩4C屏幕发黄？","answer":"1.业界的手机品牌如Iphone、三星、OPPO，VIVO等, 对显示屏最佳的色温选择都不一致，需要结合选用的显示技术及世界各地不同地域人群对显示屏色温的喜好来定义。\n2.荣耀畅玩4C结合亚洲人偏爱冷色调的习惯，将屏幕的色温做了调节。\n另外：为了优化屏幕显示效果，6月（2015）初发布了新的版本，海思平台（移动版、移动定制版、移动/联通双4G版）是B122版本，高通平台（电信定制版）是B120版本，可通过HOTA推送升级，未收到推送的可前去EMUI官网下载相应SD卡包升级。","faqTypeId":134,"faqType":"硬件与外观","useful":5,"unUseful":12,"languageId":2,"languageName":"zh_cn","faqCode":"937","faqTypeCode":"Handsets-Hardware-Appearance","isTop":"0","moduleCode":"faq","productId":null,"productCode":null,"postDate":1433498675000,"seriesProductName":"CHM-CL00,CHM-TL00,CHM-TL00H,CHM-UL00","visitedTimes":2715,"isUsefulFlag":null,"score":0,"times":0,"imageList":null,"displayType":"text","justView":"2","fileName":null,"filePath":null,"imagePath":null,"imageName":null,"productIdList":null,"curPage":null,"pageSize":null,"siteCode":null,"statusFlag":"Publish","returnCode":0,"totalRows":null,"keywords":"荣耀畅玩4C,屏幕,发黄","avgScore":0.0,"createDate":null,"totalPages":null}